Say '''Pavia''' et kumadwa ya klase baley ed luyag na [[Iloilo]], [[Pilipinas]]. Unong ed 2010 Census, say papulasyon to et 43,614 totoo. Walay kabaleg tan sukat to ya 27.15 sq. km. Sikato et walad kumadwa ya distrito. Say zip code to et 5001.	
															
